desc.Description:
This 4-star hotel directly on Lake Wolfgang offers free WiFi and a balcony in each room. The private beach with deck chairs is a 10-minute walk away. Seehotel Huber’s bright, individually decorated rooms offer traditional wooden furniture, satellite TV, and a bathroom. The restaurant serves Austrian cuisine and specialities from the Salzkammergut region, including fresh fish from the lake. Free private parking is available on site. St. Wolfgang can be reached with a ferry leaving just 200 metres away, and St. Gilgen is 5 km away. 
Disclaimer notification: Amenities are subject to availability and may be chargeable as per the hotel policy.

desc.Description:
Just 150 metres from Lake Wolfgang, Gästehaus Kloibergütl offers a private beach with deckchairs, free bicycle hire, and free WiFi in the entire property. The terrace and the balconies in all apartments overlook the lake. The spacious and bright apartments include satellite TV, a kitchen, a seating area, and a bathroom with hairdryer. Guests of the Kloibergütl can relax in a sauna, a steam bath, and an infrared cabin. The garden includes a sunbathing lawn and a childrens playground. Free private parking is available on site. Postalm, the nearest ski area, is within a 30-minute drive. Payment before arrival via bank transfer is required. The property will contact you after you book to provide instructions. This property will not accommodate hen, stag or similar parties. In response to Coronavirus (COVID-19), additional safety and sanitation measures are in effect at this property. desc.Description:
Landhaus Leitner is located directly on the shore of Lake Wolfgang and offers a private beach with a sunbathing lawn. Free WiFi access, and free parking are available. Surrounded by a 3,000 m² garden, Landhaus Leitner am Wolfgangsee offers spacious apartments with direct lake or mountain views. A bathing raft and pedal boats are available free of charge, and stand up paddling is also offered on site. St. Wolfgang, Bad Ischl, and the other attractions in the Salzkammergut region are only a short drive away from Landhaus Leitner. Between January and March the Postalm Ski Pass can be purchased on site. Please inform Landhaus Leitner am Wolfgangsee in advance of your expected arrival time. You can use the Special Requests box when booking, or contact the property directly with the contact details provided in your confirmation. This property will not accommodate hen, stag or similar parties.

desc.Description:
Pension Schlömmer is located 4 km from Sankt Gilgen and has a private beach access to Lake Wolfgang, just 200 metres from the house. It offers free bicycles for guests and a balcony in every room. Guests have free access to a sauna and an infrared cabin with panoramic mountain and lake views. Free WiFi is available. In summer, the Schlömmer Pension provides sun loungers and sunshades on the garden terrace. Guests have free access to the Seebad Abersee public beach, 200 metres away. Most of the rooms and the breakfast room were renovated in 2015. All rooms offer satellite TV, a minibar, and a bathroom with hairdryer. Breakfast is available every morning in the new breakfast room and in nice weather, guests can have breakfast on the terrace, providing panoramic mountain views. The Postalm Ski Area can be reached in 20 minutes by car. The ski bus stops 500 metres down the road. Please inform Pension Schlömmer in advance of your expected arrival time. You can use the Special Requests box when booking, or contact the property directly with the contact details provided in your confirmation. In the event of an early departure, the property will charge you the full amount for your stay. A damage deposit of EUR 500 is required on arrival. This will be collected by credit card. You should be reimbursed within 7 days of check-out. Your deposit will be refunded in full via credit card, subject to an inspection of the property.

desc.Description:
Haus Wolfgangsee is located 100 metres from the banks of the Wolfgangsee lake and features its own beach with sun beds and free WiFi, which is also available throughout the property. All of the spacious apartments have a fully equipped kitchen including a dishwasher and a microwave, a flat-screen satellite TV and a balcony or a terrace. Breakfast or a delivery service for fresh bread rolls are available on request. The Zwölferhorn cable car is 4 km away from the Haus Wolfgangsee. Hiking and cycling trails start directly outside of Haus Wolfangsee. You can visit the city of Salzburg, which can be reached within a half-hour drive, or explore the scenic Salzkammergut region by rental bike. A private spa area can be used near Haus Wolfgangsee on request and against a surcharge. Please inform Haus Wolfgangsee in advance of your expected arrival time. You can use the Special Requests box when booking, or contact the property directly with the contact details provided in your confirmation. Surrounded by a 10,000 m² garden with a large sunbathing lawn, Hotel Carossa bed&breakfast in Abersee is just a 10-minute walk from the shore of Lake Wolfgang and a private beach that guests can use free of charge. Free WiFi is available. The Salzkammergut Bicycle Trail is close by, and the towns of St. Gilgen and Strobl are both an 8-minute drive away. 
Disclaimer notification: Amenities are subject to availability and may be chargeable as per the hotel policy.

Only 600 metres away from the shore of Lake Wolfgang, the 3 star superior Hotel Gasthof Aberseehof is set in a quiet location with scenic views of the surroundings. It offers a restaurant serving traditional Austrian specialities. The spacious and bright rooms and suites all come with a balcony, a TV, a seating area, and a bathroom with shower and toilet. For children there is a playground on site, and guests of the Aberseehof have free access to a private sunbathing lawn at the lake. The area surrounding Hotel Aberseehof is ideal for hiking, cycling and mountain biking, as well as for every kind of water sports, from surfing, sailing and water skiing to swimming and diving. The Salzkammergutradweg, a bicycle trail, is accessible directly from the property. In winter the nearby Postalm Ski Area offers ideal conditions for beginners and families.

desc.Description:
This traditional, family-run inn is located directly on Lake Wolfgang, on the road between St. Gilgen and Strobl. Guests can swim, fish and use a rowboat at the private beach. Seegasthof Gamsjaga’s restaurant serves Austrian cuisine and Salzkammergut specialities such as fish from the lake and apple strudel. There is a big lakeside terrace in summer. Guests of the Gamsjaga can use a free internet terminal. The surrounding area offers ideal conditions for many activities, including sailing, fishing, hiking, Nordic walking and diving (diving school next door). The Zwölferhorn Cable Car is 5 minutes by car and Bad Ischl can be reached by car in 20 minutes. Salzburg is 35 km away. Please inform Seegasthof Gamsjaga in advance about the total number of guests (adults and children).

Just 400 metres from the shore of Lake Wolfgang, Appartementhaus Huber in Abersee offers a private beach with sun beds. The spacious apartments all have a balcony overlooking the mountains. Free WiFi is available in public areas. The rustically furnished apartments at the Huber Appartementhaus feature a living room with satellite TV, a kitchen or kitchenette with a dining area, and a bathroom. Free private parking is available on site and a lockable bike storage room. The stop of the ferry to St. Wolfgang is 400 metres away, and 2 restaurants are within 500 metres. Bad Ischl is 20 km away, and it is 25 km to the Postalm Ski Area. A ski bus stops 1 km away. Pets are warmly welcomed. Payment before arrival via bank transfer is required. The property will contact you after you book to provide instructions. This property will not accommodate hen, stag or similar parties. In response to Coronavirus (COVID-19), additional safety and sanitation measures are in effect at this property. A deposit via bank wire is required to secure your reservation when booking without a credit card. Appartementhaus Huber will contact you with instructions after booking.

desc.Description:
Overlooking Lake Wolfgang, Loitzbauer Ferienwohnungen enjoys a quiet location in the village of Abersee, only 200 metres from the shores. It offers bright and spacious apartments and private lake access. The famous and very traditional Christmas Markets in St. Gilgen, Strobl and St. Wolfgang can be reached within 15 km and are accessible by ferry, car and public bus. The bus stops 700 metres from the Loitzbauer guesthouse, the ferry pier is 900 metres away. Guests can relax in the large garden, which also provides a children’s playground, or get active at the Postalm ski area 7 km away. Mountain biking as well as cross-country skiing trails are nearby. The famous city of Salzburg is 30 km from the guesthouse and can be reached by public bus. The spa town Bad Ischl and the Kaiservilla Emperor’s Villa are 15 km away. Parking is free of charge at Loitzbauer Ferienwohnungen. Managed by a private host

Located on the edge of Abersee, Kloiberbauer is a 5-minute walk from its own private beach area at the shore of Lake Wolfgang. It provides apartments with satellite TV and a balcony with mountain views. St. Gilgen is 5 km away. The apartment comprises a living room with an open-plan kitchen, a sofa bed and a bathroom with a shower and a hairdryer. Kloiberbauer features a garden with a terrace and sun loungers. Guests can make use of the barbecue facilities while children can romp around on the playground. A covered parking space for bikes is provided and the apartment house also features a ski storage room. A toboggan run starts next to the house. The closest ski area Postalm is a 30-minute drive away. Bad Ischl can be reached within 15 minutes by car and Strobl is 8 km away. Free parking is available on site.

Located directly on the shore of Lake Wolfgang, Haus Seehof offers rooms with balconies and panoramic views of the lake and the mountains. The Postalm ski area can be easily reached by car. Each room has satellite TV and a bathroom with a hairdryer. A varied breakfast buffet is served in the morning. Haus Seehof has a large garden with a sunbathing lawn and a children’s playground. A restaurant serving regional cuisine is next to the Seehof. Haus Seehof has a free parking lot and a storage room for bicycles. Hiking and bicycle trails are nearby. Salzburg can be reached within a 30-minute drive, the imperial town Bad Ischl is a 15-minute drive away. Please inform Haus Seehof in advance of your expected arrival time.
